"description" = "In a world where AI is reshaping every industry, Prooffd helps you find the careers and businesses it can't touch.\n\nProoffd is a personalized discovery platform that matches you to 200+ AI-resistant career paths and side businesses based on your skills, budget, experience, and lifestyle. No generic advice. No guesswork. Just a clear picture of where your real opportunities live.\n\nFIND YOUR AI-PROOF MATCH\nStart with a short, personalized quiz. Prooffd analyzes your answers and surfaces the paths most likely to thrive in an AI-driven economy — complete with AI Safety Zone ratings that show exactly how resistant each opportunity is to automation and displacement.\n\nKNOW THE REAL NUMBERS\nEvery match comes with market rate data, estimated startup costs, time-to-first-dollar projections, and pricing guidance. Prooffd gives you honest, grounded information so you can evaluate opportunities with confidence and clarity.\n\nBUILD IT STEP BY STEP\nOnce you find a path worth pursuing, Prooffd walks you through it. Step-by-step build plans break the journey into manageable actions, with progress tracking, completion milestones, and a built-in encouragement system to keep you moving forward.\n\nSTAY IN MOTION\nDaily micro-actions, streaks, achievements, and a leveling system make progress feel real — even on the days when big goals feel far away. Prooffd is designed to celebrate every small win along the way.\n\nEXPLORE EDUCATION AND TRAINING PATHS\nThe Explore tab surfaces trade schools, certifications, and education pathways across healthcare, technology, business, and creative fields — so you can build the credentials your next chapter needs.\n\nGO FURTHER WITH PRO\nUnlock marketing scripts, outreach templates, financial projections, expansion strategies, and PDF exports with a Prooffd Pro subscription. Pro is built for career changers, side-hustle seekers, and anyone serious about turning a plan into action.\n\nSHARE YOUR PROGRESS\nCelebrate your results with social share cards designed for Instagram, TikTok, and LinkedIn. Your quiz matches, top paths, and build milestones are all shareable in a single tap.\n\nProoffd is a planning and discovery tool. It provides pathways, frameworks, and guidance — your outcomes depend on the effort and circumstances you bring to the process.\n\nWhether you're rethinking your career, exploring a side income stream, or simply future-proofing your options, Prooffd helps you take the first step — and every step after that.\n\nDownload Prooffd. Discover where you're built to go.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://gist.github.com/m5cp/b63e5a206cd0b4b5366f9d46c8b791b7\nApple EULA: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/ \nAccessibility: https://gist.github.com/m5cp/70b771aaf4256df02b07d4a76f44aa99";
